{
  "stem": "18056.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 153.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was only eight-- eight miles or so, so you-- we went in the trolley car.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we took our little things, whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we were living with some relatives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans came in and they said, [GERMAN], you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By Monday morning, you are not here in this town anymore, period.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to move to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we were in Lodz, it was, of course, right away the situation with the ghetto that there's a ghetto being built.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so everyone was running into the area where the-- where the ghetto is going to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is how the ghetto was built.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, more and more people came in and then they-- there was not enough room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In some apartments where there was maybe you could have only three or four people living, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they would put in eight, eight people, double the amount.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, we-- at that time, we had to live-- we lived I think it was three or four families in one large room, maybe as as large as this room, maybe a little bigger.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we just divided it up with a sheet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each one had their own little facilities, where they had their bed to sleep on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes you had-- in one bed, you had two-- two-- two children, the husband, and the wife, or there were six or seven children in there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some people slept during the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people slept during the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
